華為美國子公司被控在 2012 年至 2014 年間合謀盜取了 T-Mobile 美國公司一項名為「Tappy」的技術。「Tappy」的技術用於模仿人類手指，用於測試智能手機。華為一名員工被指曾拆下機械臂，甚至量度和拍照記錄，其後把資料傳回中國。華為指該名員工是獨立行事，之後已被革職。華為表示，已與 T-Mobile 在 2017 年和解。<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21dd2488a67d602316109a87472d70d39553b77f","tid":1041631,"uid":61280,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T03:35:52.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">等睇鳩吹：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5G冇我地，就如NBA冇左Raptors！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"efd72e3d0ca411efbee7ae89602da64ce2e921a0","tid":1041631,"uid":25424,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T03:37:22.000Z","msg":"人哋三權分立<br />\n指控係無理嘅話法庭自然判你無罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同支那人講法治真係戇柒鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a84b689ab8e8236585ba83325bb1d66db283952c","tid":1041631,"uid":3167,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T03:43:37.000Z","msg":"美國人中國心咩戇撚柒鳩<br />\n都唔撚用腦<br />\n唔企國家個邊信你支那狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"e781d7fb56189ee60b0cd02045419e7df83ac8fb","tid":1041631,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21dd2488a67d602316109a87472d70d39553b77f","tid":1041631,"uid":61280,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T03:35:52.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">等睇鳩吹：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5G冇我地，就如NBA冇左Raptors！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T03: